<view class="page">
  <view class="page-header">
    <view>
      <view class="eyebrow">PROFILE</view>
      <view class="title">我的</view>
    </view>
  </view>

  <view class="placeholder-card">
    <view class="placeholder-icon">◉</view>
    <view class="placeholder-title">本期"我的"为占位</view>
    <view class="placeholder-desc">
      账号信息 · 收益结算 · 邀请关系 · 设置 等能力将在小程序后续版本上线。
      运营/审核能力均在 admin 后台（apps/admin）。
    </view>
    <view class="placeholder-info mono">
      <text>token: {{tokenMasked}}</text>
      <text>activationCode: {{auth.activationCode}}</text>
      <text>phone: {{auth.phone}}</text>
    </view>
    <view class="placeholder-cta" bindtap="logout">退出登录</view>
  </view>
</view>
